D. Acquisition Strategy
In order to meet accelerated timelines, the QS-ER wing kit and tail kit are being procured under a sole source contract with Boeing. QS-ER leak resistant bomb bodies
are being procured through a sole source contract with REPKON USA. QS MOD 3 and CDM mine kits, including target detecting devices, adapters, other hardware
components and the Mine Delivery System are procured via various small contract vehicles or developed internally by the Government. All mine component software for
QS MOD 3 and CDM is developed and maintained by Government activities. QS-ER wing kit software is proprietary to Boeing.




