D. Acquisition Strategy
In order to meet accelerated timelines for hardware, the development of the QS-LR payload delivery units and their associated support equipment are being developed
and procured under a sole source contract with Boeing administered by USAF. The Mk 62 500lb Quickstrike mine is the payload used in the QS-LR all-up-round (AUR)
and will be drawn from in-service stock.




