 8. Adaptable Deck Launcher (ADL): Replacing the aging MK 29 launcher, ADL doubles missile capacity on capital ships (CVN, LHA, and LHD), improves sustainability,
 and enhances maintainability. The new launching system will allow significantly more flexibility for ESSM Blk 1 and Blk 2 in different loadout configurations with available
 inventory. It will support both ESSM Blk 1 and Blk 2 in flexible configurations. The ADL replacement contains design margin to allow for ESSM evolutionary growth within
 the MK25 canister.

