Marine Air/Ground Task Force. As a high-speed, amphibious craft, it projects power by being fully compatible with all allied amphibious ships, while performing assaults
and operational maneuvers from ship to shore and across the beach. SSC provides the functional replacement for the Landing Craft, Air Cushion (LCAC) Class of ships,
