A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
The Management HQ - R&D program funds management headquarter civilian personnel salaries at the Office of Naval Research (ONR). These personnel support the
management of the Naval Science and Technology (S&T) programs. This program also funds management headquarter contractor support for the Integrated Warfare
Systems (IWS) Program Executive Office.

