D. Acquisition Strategy
The ADC MK5 program is currently in the E&MD phase. The ADC MK5 acquisition strategy is to continue funding Leidos to produce and deliver test articles that will
support developmental and operational testing. Follow-on production contracts will be awarded to provide sufficient inventory to meet Fleet objectives.

The ADC MK6 acquisition strategy is to competitively award Other Transaction Agreements to begin development (hardware and software) and prototyping efforts which
will continue throughout the FYDP.




