Description: This funding provides for the development of a software based solution into the Mission Computer
of the F/A-18E/F and EA-18G platforms, with the capability to detect intrusion and malicious network behaviors.
The capability determines suspect malicious behavior via real time network traffic analysis. Aircrew are alerted
to take action and quarantine the effects of affected subsystems, permitting the opportunity to degrade rather
than deny platform capability. The capability provides a positive method to ensure mission aircraft systems
integrity during a cyber-hostile wartime network environment.

FY 2026 Plans:
