directly supports the Collaborative IAMD Planning Program (CIPP) and provides collaborative cyclic planning in support of Carrier Strike Group Operations supporting
Distributed Maritime Operations (DMO) and is the Navy's only multi-baseline / multi-ship Integrated Air and Missile Defense (IAMD) Planner.

