A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This Congressional Add provides for the demonstration of a ship-integrated coaxial drone prototype for autonomous Intelligence, Surveillance and Reconnaissance
(ISR). This project will integrate Command and Control (C2), rigorous on-shore testing, and a final proof-of-concept demonstration within a representative fleet
operational environment. The project directly supports the Chief of Naval Operations' objectives for Joint All-Domain Command and Control (JADC2) objectives in
preparation for a 2027 peer or near-peer conflict.

