FY 2026 Plans:
This effort will continue the development of integrated beam expanders, advanced adaptive optics, and advanced laser quality
track subsystems and technologies, ensuring tactical readiness in a directed energy beam control system. This effort will begin
developing a demonstration strategy for subsystems to enhance and validate performance metrics. It will optimize the subsystem
level designs to deliver a mission relevant design specification.
